<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="113" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[140,1108,166,510]" pageId="8" pageNumber="113">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[185,283,413,439]" pageId="8" pageNumber="113">
<emphasis box="[185,278,413,439]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="113" reason="1">Biology</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
Nothing is known of the biology of this species. 
<bibRefCitation author="Krikken J" box="[870,1050,413,439]" pageId="8" pageNumber="113" pagination="1 - 75" refId="ref9110" refString="Krikken J (1984) A new key to the suprageneric taxa in the beetle family Cetoniidae, with annotated lists of the known genera. Zoologische Verhandelingen. 210: 1 - 75." type="journal article" year="1984">Krikken (1984)</bibRefCitation>
